    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b39a",
      "text": "(5.3) Tuning for busy people",
      "created": 1556173042,
      "updated": 1556173043,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b39b",
      "text": "I have described all the steps of the KJ method in the previous sections.",
      "created": 1556173048,
      "updated": 1556173075,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b39c",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1556173071,
      "updated": 1556173071,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b39d",
      "text": "Jiro Kawakita is an anthropologist. In other words, he can use a long time to organize ideas.",
      "created": 1556173071,
      "updated": 1556173078,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b39e",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1556173071,
      "updated": 1556173071,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b39f",
      "text": "On the other hand, many readers of this book are busy. The lack of time constantly plagues us. So I think the original KJ method does not fit our situation. If the situation changes, we need to design a methodology accordingly. As I said in [(0.1.1) What is Intellectual Production], [The optimal way to boost creativity depends on your situation, so you need to build it by yourself.]",
      "created": 1556173071,
      "updated": 1556173123,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b3a0",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1556173071,
      "updated": 1556173071,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b3a1",
      "text": "In this section, I discuss how to modify the KJ method to do in a limited, fragmentary time.",
      "created": 1556173071,
      "updated": 1556173128,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b3a2",
